data.message: Dear Eminem , Today im sick . and just listening ur songs <3 that makes me feel better :)) <3 Em, would you plz ask a questions again here .. if u do that im very much happy and never miss that again :'( <3 just tryna notice me .. and you know Em i love you i love you idol .. and Eminem i  cant go to the rapture ... :'( ugh . just need you to tour in Philippines .. <3 that would be very great :) <3 Em.. im listening to ur song 'hello' (relapse) <3 my fav.. ;) xD hehehe next is 'cold wind blows' <3 Idol so bye now .. hope u have a great day.. love you <3 :* and tc <3 :) ur stan--- Elizabeth tupaz <3
